![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c6df990b-e971-4269-983f-2aa0c0e6ba79/e263.jpg)

It's the FINAL EPISODE of the Major Issues Podcast for 2022! Join us as we look back at one hell of a year and go over some of the best and worse releases in it! From The Batman to Wakanda Forever, see how some of your favorites stack up in this deep dive discussion of all things 2022! We also want to thank everyone who joined us for the first time in 2022! Let's make 2023 UNFORGETTABLE!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

